Cards & Castles 2, I'm gonna refer to it's as C&C2 for the rest of this website so I don't get a headache, is a tactical card game for IOS, Android, and Steam. In it you create decks of 30 cards and battle against opponents online using strategies of board placement, movement, card usage, spell use and much more to destroy your opponent's castle. The game is both simple to pick up and hard to master with several strong and unique strategies only possible in this game. If this has you intrigued as a newcomer or you're just a long time veteran looking to learn a little then this site is for you! Browse this website of guides and tips as you may and have fun!
